# AIOS knowledge records and the generated adapters are content-hashed by the
# `aios` CLI. Pin LF so those checksums stay stable across platforms: with
# Windows core.autocrlf=true, a checkout would rewrite them to CRLF and make
# `aios validate` report the adapters as stale even though nothing changed.
ai/** text eol=lf
AGENTS.md text eol=lf
CLAUDE.md text eol=lf
